window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>They say that confession is necessary to purify the soul. However, there are some deeds that are so sinister, so wicked, that even the most remorseful admission of guilt is not enough to atone for them. </p> <p>From the mind of Vincent V. Cava comes his most twisted book to date: Nine frightening stories told through the voices of those who witnessed them. These terrifying tales will horrify and sicken you. For those lovers of grim, supernatural fiction, <i>Dark Anonymous Confessions</i> is a must-listen. </p>"; 
